msgctxt "924"
msgid "Gossipy Wife"
msgstr "Esposa Chismosa"

msgctxt "928"
msgid "Jabbery Husband"
msgstr "Esposo Parlanchín"

msgctxt "84_Gossipy Wife"
msgid "[Mei Hua-chan's such a good girl. She's half the reason people come to this restaurant.]"
msgstr "[Mei Huita-chan es un encanto. Mucha gente viene a este restaurante por ella.]"

msgctxt "96_Jabbery Husband"
msgid "[Indeed. She's so cheerful and considerate. It makes me happy just seeing her.]"
msgstr "[Exacto. Ella es tan simpática y considerada. Con solo verla se me alegra el día.]"

msgctxt "108_Gossipy Wife"
msgid "[She's the kind of girl I'd like our son to marry.]"
msgstr "[Ella es el tipo de chica con la que me gustaría que nuestro\n"\n"hijo se casara.]"

msgctxt "120_Jabbery Husband"
msgid "[Our son is only five!]"
msgstr "[¡Nuestro hijo apenas tiene cinco años!]"

msgctxt "132_Gossipy Wife"
msgid "[Yes, but older women make the best wives. That's why our marriage works so well, don't you think?]"
msgstr "[Sí, pero las maduritas son excelentes esposas. Por eso nuestro matrimonio funciona tan bien, ¿no te parece?]"

msgctxt "144_Jabbery Husband"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

